OL,3,CMan who manipulated grandparents out
OL,4,Cof thousands of pounds is jailed
OL,6,FOn one occasion he claimed it was for
OL,7,Fprivate cancer treatment.
OL,9,FHe started by taking his grandfather
OL,10,Fto a bank to withdraw thousands of
OL,11,Fpounds at a time.
OL,13,FHowever after the bank stopped this,
OL,14,Fhe would encourage his grandfather to
OL,15,Fget cashback from local supermarkets
OL,16,Fbefore arranging to meet him to make
OL,17,Fmore withdrawals.
OL,19,FTilden was arrested in November 2023
OL,20,Fand bailed while enquiries continued.
