OL,6,FPolice say he repeatedly broke bail
OL,7,Fconditions which required him not to
OL,8,Fvisit his grandparents.
OL,10,FHe was then re-arrested and charged
OL,11,Fwith controlling or coercive behaviour
OL,12,Fin an intimate or family relationship
OL,13,Funder section 76 of the Serious Crime
OL,14,FAct having manipulated his
OL,15,Fgrandparents into giving him a total
OL,16,Fof #384,077.
