OL,3,CMan who manipulated grandparents out
OL,4,Cof thousands of pounds is jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement, his grandfather said
OL,7,Fhe was scared to say no to Tilden,
OL,8,Fdescribing his home life as like being
OL,9,F'under siege' due to the constant
OL,10,Fvisits.
OL,12,FPC Sarah Hardwidge, based in Devizes,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This was a complex
OL,14,Finvestigation which the Devizes
OL,15,FNeighbourhood Policing Team worked on
OL,16,Ffor three years.
