OL,6,F"It was through partnership working
OL,7,Fwith medical professionals, adult
OL,8,Fsocial care, banks and local shops
OL,9,Fthat we were able to gather the
OL,10,Fevidence required and safeguard the
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,F"Daniel's offending behaviour towards
OL,14,Fhis grandparents was appalling. He
OL,15,Ftook advantage of their good nature
OL,16,Fand has caused them lasting distress
OL,17,Fin their own home.
