OL,6,F"We would also like to thank the CPS
OL,7,Fand the courts for recognising the
OL,8,Fseriousness of this crime which is
OL,9,Freflected in the sentence given.
OL,11,F"We're extremely pleased and relieved
OL,12,Fat the outcome as it has brought peace
OL,13,Fto the victims and protected them from
OL,14,Ffurther abuse."
OL,16,FTilden appeared at Swindon Crown Court
OL,17,Fon Wednesday 24 April and was
OL,18,Fsentenced to three years and nine
OL,19,Fmonths imprisonment.
